item.title: Jar Maker..webclient
item.dc:creator: @toxic-x toxic-x
item.description:
@toxic-x wrote:

making a jar web client is very very very easy…

Make sure your manifest is client.java
when you uploaded your cache to dropbox did you copy all the files in the cache folder and not the folder itself?
Have you checked your signlink to see if your cache is where its suppose to be.

ALSO MAKE SURE YOU PUT UR ACTUAL JARFILE IN DROPBOX COPY PUBLIC LINK AND PASTE IN SPACE PROVIDED IN THE HTML.
